  "title": "Front Desk Officer (Hotel Industry)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Provide personalized service to guests and promptly handle their requests to ensure a seamless stay experience.</li>\n  <li>Perform cashiering duties and carefully manage the cash float.</li>\n  <li>Answer incoming and outgoing calls in a professional manner.</li>\n  <li>Promote the property's upselling programs.</li>\n  <li>Assist guests with inquiries regarding transportation, directions, restaurant reservations, and other services.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma in Hotel Management, or a related field.</li>\n  <li>Minimum 1 year front office/ customer service of experience in hotel industry.</li>\n  <li>Excellent communication and presentation skills</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Interested applicants for the above advertised position(s), please kindly email an updated copy of your resume to: <strong>gs1@talenttradersg.com;</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>EA License No.: 13C6305</p>\n<p>Registration No.: R23117856 CHOE KIN MUN</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>For candidate who applied for the advertised position is deemed to have consented to us that we may collect, use or disclose your personal information for purpose in connection with the services provided by us.</p>",
